name: INAUGURAL FLIGHT - Edelweiss Air A330-343 [HB-JHR] Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
After a 4-year hiatus, Swiss leisure airline Edelweiss Air has returned to Calgary for twice-weekly summer service. Starting today until September, YYC will be served with a mix of A330-200 and -300 aircraft. Seen here is one of Edelweiss' A330-300s arriving on runway 35R and taxiing up close. ATC is included as well. Enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
____________________________________________________
